original: Lundin, Bo Axel Erik, tandläkare, Jönköping, f. 24/10/98 i Jönköp. av dir. Josef L. o. Ebba Almstedt. G. 36 m. Stina Skårin. Barn: Håkan f 38, Christer 40, Elisabeth 43. — Stud:ex. i Jönköp. 19, med. stud. i Upps. 31-32, tandl :kand. 33, tandl:ex. 36. Tandl :prakt. i Jönköp. sed. 36, skol-tandl. i Huskvarna 37-46, tandl. v. Vrlhetosro anst. f. fallandesjuka 38-39. Anst. på adv:kont. 20-30.
translated: Lundin, Bo Axel Erik, dentist, Jönköping, b. 24/10/98 in Jönköping. Son of director Josef L. and Ebba Almstedt. Married in 1936 to Stina Skårin. Children: Håkan, born in 1938, Christer, born in 1940, Elisabeth, born in 1943. Completed high school in Jönköping in 1919. Medical studies in Uppsala from 1931-1932. Dental studies: degree in dental medicine in 1933, dental license in 1936. Worked as a dentist in Jönköping since 1936, school dentist in Huskvarna from 1937-1946. Employed at Vrlhetosro for epilepsy treatment from 1938-1939. Worked at a law firm from 1920-1930.
